steps.description:
Write end-to-end integration test `e2e_parse_compile_eval_auto_param`: parse source `structure S {
  param x : Scalar = auto
  param y : Scalar = 5mm
  let z = y * 2
  constraint x > 2mm
}`, compile, eval, check. Assert: no parse errors, x is ValueCellKind::Auto, x is (Undef, Auto) in snapshot, y is evaluated to 0.005 SI, z = 0.01 SI, constraint on x is Indeterminate.
